{"contact":{"id":"contact","heading":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Contact</strong></b></p>","visible":true,"photo":"","name":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">胡书畅</strong></b></p>","phone":"123-456-7890","email":"123@elegantresume.com","address":"abc street, Toronto, ON, Can","website":"www.yourwebsite.com","showIcon":true,"items":[{"id":"1","field":"phone","name":"phone","visible":true},{"id":"2","field":"email","name":"email","visible":true},{"id":"3","field":"address","name":"address","visible":true},{"id":"4","field":"website","name":"website","visible":false}],"contactInfo":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">男｜本科｜25｜嵌入式软件工程师｜2 年工作经验｜18758924720｜</span><a href=\"mailto:https:/github.com/ybyllc\" class=\"editor-link\"><u><span class=\"editor-text-underline\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">https://github.com/ybyllc</span></u></a></p>","freeInput":false},"summary":{"id":"summary","heading":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Summary</strong></b></p>","visible":false,"content":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Explain your qualification for the job in 1-3 sentences. Mention your current situation and years of experience and show recruiters how your skills will fit this position at the company you are applying for. Example: Energetic and passionate college student working towards a BS in Marketing at the University of Abcdef. Gained expertise in data analysis, publication marketing, web based advertising, and brand consulting. Aiming to use my knowledge of advertising, PR, product development, and consumer research strategies to satisfy the marketing internship at your company.</span></p>"},"experience":{"id":"experience","heading":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">工作经历</strong></b></p>","visible":true,"items":[{"experienceId":"506dbd3f-0c62-41eb-9e22-4b59c6d2bd3f","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":true,\"date\":true,\"location\":false}","jobTitle":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">四方集团</strong></b></p>","company":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">移动机器人（农机）嵌入式开发</strong></b></p>","location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>","hideStartDate":false,"date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"2025.10","endDate":"2026.04","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">预研新一代农机平台，上层使用ROS2 + 激光雷达，下层操控STM32通信完成底盘控制和传感器数据滤波和汇总。使用CAN通信进行协同，外接农机的执行机构</span></li><li value=\"2\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">负责水田除草机项目，采用边缘计算摄像头配合yolo v11n自训练模型识别追踪水稻的位置，结合陀螺仪信息实现水田场景的遍历。电子实验室的搭建和管理</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true},{"experienceId":"5f99f026-3c2b-47f9-a749-bda39128637a","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":true,\"date\":true,\"location\":false}","jobTitle":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">新华三集团 OD</strong></b></p>","company":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">嵌入式 Linux 开发</strong></b></p>","location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Toronto, ON</span></p>","hideStartDate":false,"date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"2024.06","endDate":"2025.09","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">年度绩效A级，多次荣获部门问题单月度冠军，获新华三\"英卡瑞吉\"专项嘉奖</span></li><li value=\"2\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">入职 2 个月独立负责山西省份的通信维护，学习能力和效率突出。负责新人的培训</span></li><li value=\"3\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">基于联发科 SoC 开发 Linux 平台实现软件功能，实现多进程间通信，网络协议调试和前后端通信</span></li><li value=\"4\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">修复系统 </span><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">bug </strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">200+，优化系统任务队列，优化设备启动流程，负责PPPoE</span><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">拨号</span><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">功能开发和维护</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">，修复PPPoE挤占系统任务队列的问题。使用 tcpdump 和 wireshark 抓包来解决网络协议问题</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true}]},"education":{"id":"education","heading":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">教育背景</strong></b></p>","visible":true,"items":[{"educationId":"273015e0-d480-4aeb-a40e-61539eb43dc2","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":true,\"date\":true,\"location\":false}","degree":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">杭州电子科技大学信息工程学院｜本科&nbsp;</strong></b></p>","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"2020.09","hideStartDate":false,"endDate":"2024.06","institution":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">电子信息工程</strong></b></p>","location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>","summaryVisibility":true,"summary":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">TI 杯</span><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">全国大学生电子设计竞赛  全国一等奖</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">（2023 年，队长）</span></li><li value=\"2\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">浙江省大学生电子设计竞赛  三等奖（2022 年）</span></li><li value=\"3\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">全国大学生智能车竞赛  三等奖（2021 年）</span></li><li value=\"4\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">获得校奖学金等荣誉</span></li></ul>"}]},"project":{"id":"project","heading":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">项目经历</strong></b></p>","visible":true,"items":[{"projectId":"17fea41f-5756-408f-8a7d-46ea5e105b72","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":false,\"date\":true,\"location\":false}","title":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">水田除草机器人｜</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">四方集团</span></p>","subTitle":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Enter your project one-line summary here.</span></p>","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"2025.11","hideStartDate":false,"endDate":"2026.04","location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Toronto, ON</span></p>","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">负责边缘计算摄像头与yolov11n自训练模型的集成，实现水稻位置的识别与追踪。</span></li><li value=\"2\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">设计基于STM32和 RTOS的除草执行机构控制方案，通过CAN总线与农机底盘通信，实现精准作业。</span></li><li value=\"3\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">开发OSD触摸屏UI交互系统，支持路径规划、实时监控与参数配置。</span></li><li value=\"4\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">完成电机驱动板（DRV8701）的PCB设计，并跟进SMT贴片、插件焊接、功能测试等量产流程。</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true},{"projectId":"1fdd6b9f-6400-4c72-9bd1-e0c7469a85f3","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":false,\"date\":true,\"location\":false}","title":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">基于UWB 跟随的智能运货车（AMR）｜</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">本科毕业设计（优秀）</span></p>","subTitle":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"2024.02","hideStartDate":false,"endDate":"2024.06","location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Toronto, ON</span></p>","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">高精度定位与导航</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">：基于UWB+TWR算法融合陀螺仪数据，通过卡尔曼滤波优化位置估计，实现±5cm级定位精度，实现车跟随人移动的功能，为SLAM建图与路径规划提供核心数据支撑，支持实时目标跟踪。</span></li><li value=\"2\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">底盘运动控制</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">：设计麦克纳姆轮全向底盘，实现360°无死角移动；开发四轮独立PID控制算法，调优算法抑制轮子打滑，实现曲线平滑加减速，确保启停平稳，最大速度达1.2m/s。</span></li><li value=\"3\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">多传感器融合</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">：集成ICM20602陀螺仪、TOF传感器，实现避障保护和稳定运动，通过传感器数据融合提升复杂环境下的系统稳定性。</span></li><li value=\"4\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">机械臂：</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">两轴机械臂，结合视觉识别定位实现物品的抓取</span></li><li value=\"5\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">硬件设计：</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">完成单片机系统板的设计，DCDC 电源模块的设计</span></li><li value=\"6\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">嵌入式系统开发</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">：基于STM32F407+RTOS实现多任务调度（定位、控制、视觉、通信），保障系统实时性。</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true},{"projectId":"43900bfd-7925-4c40-9605-d49fef79ac8d","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":false,\"date\":true,\"location\":false}","title":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">高精度云台控制系统 ｜</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">TI 杯全国大学生电子设计竞赛 一等奖（队长）</span></p>","subTitle":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">伺服视觉系统开发</span></p>","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"2023.08","hideStartDate":true,"endDate":"2023.08","location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Toronto, ON</span></p>","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">视觉识别</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">：基于OpenCV实现色域转换+高斯滤波+霍夫变换矩形识别的目标识别，实现高精度视觉闭环。</span></li><li value=\"2\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">运动控制算法</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">：设计双环PID控制算法，针对舵机抖动问题，优化运动控制逻辑，为机器人视觉系统提供稳定平台，支撑精准目标跟踪，激光指向精度达±0.5mm</span></li><li value=\"3\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">开发效率：</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">4 天 3 夜内完成整个项目的软硬件设计和搭建，浙江省内该题评分第一，国赛获得全国一等奖</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true},{"projectId":"f9f6edd7-d1f3-4c62-ab2d-5b8649b7f215","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":false,\"date\":true,\"location\":false}","title":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">路径规划智能视觉小车 ｜ </strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">全国大学生智能车竞赛  省三等奖</span></p>","subTitle":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"2022.02","hideStartDate":false,"endDate":"2022.08","location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Toronto, ON</span></p>","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">基于 NXP  RT1064主控开发，基于 OpenART 完成视觉识别开发，实现粮食、水果、蔬菜共 15 类目标图片检测与分类，支持带框 / 无框目标板识别。</span></li><li value=\"2\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">实现 A4 纸目标点位图自动识别解析，采用蚁群算法，A*算法优化多点最短行驶路径，提升任务执行效率。设计惯性导航 + 编码器 + 磁力计融合定位方案，实现已知 / 未知区域目标自主搜索与路径规划。</span></li><li value=\"3\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">开发麦克纳姆轮PID运动控制算法，位置环+角度环+速度环，实现精准定位与移动，配合电磁铁完成目标板拾取、搬运与分类投放。</span></li><li value=\"4\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">完成整车调试与场地联调，确保车辆从车库出发、目标搜索识别、分类搬运、自动回库全流程稳定运行。</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true},{"projectId":"e6821a76-bddf-422e-9be7-175873ddc7b6","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":false,\"date\":true,\"location\":false}","title":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">双车寻迹系统</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">｜浙江省大学生电子设计竞赛  省三等奖</span></p>","subTitle":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"2021.08","hideStartDate":true,"endDate":"2022.08","location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Toronto, ON</span></p>","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">基于 TI  MSP430 和 OpenMV 摄像头，采用大津法二值化实现黑线的巡线，并且适配弯道识别和自适应速度的决策</span></li><li value=\"2\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">使用蓝牙模块和 Modbus 通信协议完成双车的通信协同，克服通信延迟，进行速度和位置的同步及路线的共享决策</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true},{"projectId":"e54fe1bb-0b66-43f7-9ddf-d71d7c9c54a8","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":false,\"date\":false,\"location\":false}","title":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">整理 STM32 代码库</strong></b><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">｜https://github.com/ybyllc/stm32-tea-lib</span></p>","subTitle":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">包含 STM32 小车常用的任务规划和传感器算法的代码库，对接 HAL 库，实现STM32 不同芯片的适配和快速开发</span></li></ul><p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><br></p>","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"Start Date","hideStartDate":true,"endDate":"End Date","location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Toronto, ON</span></p>","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">STM32 小车常用的任务规划和传感器算法的代码库，以及外设传感器适配驱动，对接 HAL 库，实现 STM32 不同芯片的快速适配和开发</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true},{"projectId":"18faea26-e7bd-4f83-8937-895038eed610","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":false,\"date\":false,\"location\":false}","title":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">无刷电机多功能旋钮</strong></b></p>","subTitle":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">位置环PD+电流环PI，实现弹簧效果和刻度效果</span></p>","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"Start Date","hideStartDate":true,"endDate":"End Date","location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Toronto, ON</span></p>","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">使用 FOC 算法，位置环PD+电流环PI，实现模拟阻尼，模拟弹簧，模拟刻度等效果</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true}]},"academicExperience":{"id":"academicExperience","heading":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">个人项目</strong></b></p>","visible":false,"items":[{"id":"e58d6eab-62df-4016-aa8a-0a898b5bead6","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"subtitle\":true,\"date\":true,\"location\":true}","title":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">机械手</strong></b></p>","subTitle":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Enter your project one-line summary here.</span></p>","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"Start Date","endDate":"End Date","hideStartDate":false,"location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Toronto, ON</span></p>","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;Provide&nbsp;details&nbsp;about&nbsp;your&nbsp;project.</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true},{"id":"30147e33-2201-4113-b16a-19e61ad12ac9","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":false,\"date\":false,\"location\":false}","title":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">无刷电机多功能旋钮</strong></b></p>","subTitle":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"Start Date","endDate":"End Date","hideStartDate":false,"location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Toronto, ON</span></p>","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">实现无刷电机的电流环控制，模拟挡位、阻尼、弹簧等场景，掌握电机驱动核心逻辑，为AGV底盘电机控制提供技术储备。</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true}]},"awards":{"id":"award","heading":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Awards</strong></b></p>","visible":false,"content":"<p>List your award here.</p>"},"skill":{"id":"skill","heading":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">个人技能</strong></b></p>","visible":true,"content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">熟练掌握 C/C++、Python编程语言，掌握 STM32/NXP/TI/ 中微 / 51 等 MCU 平台，联发科等 SoC 平台开发。有 Linux、RTOS、ROS 平台开发经验</span></li><li value=\"2\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">掌握 Linux 嵌入式开发，掌握Makefile 编写、Shell 脚本编写、交叉编译，熟练使用 Git 进行版本管理</span></li><li value=\"3\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">掌握无人车嵌入式开发，熟悉底盘运动控制，掌握运动控制算法（PID、MPC 等）、多传感器融合算法（互补滤波、卡尔曼滤波等）、路径规划算法（蚁群算法、A-star 等）</span></li><li value=\"4\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">熟练掌握 SPI、I2C、UART、 RS485等硬件外设，调试TCP/IP、CAN 总线、PPPoE等通信协议</span></li><li value=\"5\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">熟练使用 AD / 立创 EDA 设计 PCB，具备 DCDC 电源、电机驱动设计经验，拥有硬件产品的量产经验</span></li></ul>"},"customSection1":{"id":"14c426d4-fc5d-434a-82bf-c457e7c695fc","heading":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Custom Section</strong></b></p>","visible":false,"items":[{"id":"fb7aa165-e151-4e05-ad8f-68b92f213354","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":true,\"subtitle\":true,\"date\":true,\"location\":true}","title":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Please Enter A Title</strong></b></p>","subTitle":"Enter your one-line summary here.","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"Start Date","hideStartDate":false,"endDate":"End Date","location":"Toronto, ON","content":"<ul><li>&nbsp;Provide&nbsp;details&nbsp;about&nbsp;your&nbsp;project.</li></ul>","summaryVisibility":true}]},"customSection2":{"id":"f4cb4ebf-1d8f-452e-85cc-0eaade1017ad","heading":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">个人评价</strong></b></p>","visible":false,"items":[{"id":"da311736-3817-4c1b-8191-98c2e9867e43","visible":true,"fieldsVisibility":"{\"title\":false,\"subtitle\":true,\"date\":false,\"location\":false}","title":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><b><strong class=\"editor-text-bold\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Please Enter A Title</strong></b></p>","subTitle":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">优秀的软件能力以外，还具有软硬件结合的调试能力和从 0 到 1 的快速搭建工程的能力，产品转化量产经验，以及对无人车行业极大的热情</span></p>","date":"Start Date - End Date","startDate":"Start Date","hideStartDate":false,"endDate":"End Date","location":"<p class=\"editor-paragraph\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Toronto, ON</span></p>","content":"<ul class=\"editor-list-ul\"><li value=\"1\" class=\"editor-listitem\"><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;Provide&nbsp;details&nbsp;about&nbsp;your&nbsp;project.</span></li></ul>","summaryVisibility":false}]},"metadata":{"id":"metadata","heading":"metadata","resumeId":"fb933a45-79c5-4c04-825d-28a40362e2a9","language":"en","templateId":"3","font":"Lato","fontSize":"12","lineHeight":1,"fitToOnePage":false,"fitToOnePageMargin":{"mainSectionTopMargin":0,"subSectionTopMargin":0},"showGrammarly":false,"paperSize":"US Letter","layout":{"fixedBlocks":[["contact"]],"draggableBlocks":[["education","skill","experience","project","summary","academicExperience","awards","customSection1","customSection2"]]},"colors":{"primary":"#000000","text":"#000000","background":"#FFFFFF"},"dateFormat":1},"interview":{"activeQuestion":{"id":null},"questions":[]}}